{"tid":1256665,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全家擁英籍毋須放棄　林鄭：多一個旅遊證件啫","createTime":"2019-06-25T06:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T12:32:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7968698c90f7a99c177121688c2f8cfdb92b5a7c","tid":1256665,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/16804163_174634416371845_1451592611381655024_o_pI5o9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F16804163_174634416371845_1451592611381655024_o_pI5o9_1200x0.png&h=89785d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：林鄭辦公室<br />\n<br />\n特首選舉候選人林鄭月娥接受《am730》專訪時提到，丈夫林兆波及兩名兒子林節思與林約希至今仍擁有英國籍。她稱和家人於1990年透過居英權計劃取得英籍，「嗰個係所謂多一個旅遊證件嘅啫，我唔覺得佢需要放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭強調，她早於2007年出任發展局局長時已放棄英藉，將來應該不會重新申請。對於丈夫多次在街頭被記者追訪，她形容，丈夫對傳媒非常配合，「有時佢特登停落嚟，等佢哋(記者)擺好機、等佢哋叫埋同事嚟先接受訪問&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭提到自己對丈夫笑稱，「你真係好，應該入政府做，咁我哋（政府）對於傳媒關係肯定好好多。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E8%8B%B1%E7%B1%8D-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E8%AD%89%E4%BB%B6%E5%95%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%25B1%258D-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2595%25AB%2F&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443mE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=de4d806c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%25B1%258D-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580